svg.title: Sheet Music for "The Blackbird (DJN version)"

text.tspan: Notes: This is another verison of The Blackbird transcribed by my uncle. He seems to have
resolved the unusual 7.5 measures of the versions I've found to a regular 8 bars,
perhaps to make it more condusive to other forms besides the step-dance.
